npm install -g grunt cli
We need two files
  1)package.json
  2)Gruntfile.js

Install grunt command:  npm install grunt --save-dev
  --save will save it in project.
  -dev will install its dependency in package.json

  *** Install ***               *** Command ***

 1 Create package.json            npm init ****
 2 Install grunt                  npm install -g grunt-cli
 3 Install grunt-contrib-less     npm install grunt-contrib-less --save-dev
 4 Install grunt-contrib-watch    npm install grunt-contrib-watch
 5 Install grunt-contrib-jshint   npm install grunt-contrib-jshint

  ***

